docs.text:
Networking


Automatic Location


Use 
locationchanger
 to automatically change OS's network location based on the name of the Wi-Fi network I am connected to.


Installation:


curl -L https://github.com/eprev/locationchanger/raw/master/locationchanger.sh | bash
